cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and connection establishment rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting global_log_level to an invalid value 'invalid' will cause logging configuration errors during startup.
du.explanation_zh: 將 global_log_level 設定為無效值 'invalid' 會在啟動期間導致日誌配置錯誤。
